  <brief_title>Microbiological Spectrum of the Intraperitoneal Surface After Elective Right-sided Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Microbiological Spectrum of the Intraperitoneal Surface After Elective Right-sided Colon Cancer: Are There Differences in the Peritoneal Contamination After Performing a Stapled or a Handsewn Anastomosis?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
